Eigenvalues 290 Eigenvalues and Eigenvectors........................ 290 Properties of Eigenvalues and Eigenvectors................ 308 Similarity and Diagonalization....................... 318 
Linear Transformations 331 Linear Transformations........................... 331 Injective Linear Transformations...................... 351 Surjective Linear Transformations..................... 364 Invertible Linear Transformations...................... 378 
